works.description: Martell, one of the oldest of big cognac houses, has now teamed up with Pinel & Pinel, the French house famous for its contemporary and bespoke trunks, to create a unique trunk. Pinel & Pinel has designed a special mobile trunk case, the largest ever from the house. It is 2.06 meters high, 2.20 meters wide and 0.70 meters deep.
